{{Quote|And you thought swoopbike racing was a scary sport &mdash; these guys do this sort of thing for fun!|Birdigan Nasalle|<ref name="The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref>}}
'''Birdigan Nasalle''' was a [[Swooper/Legends|swoop racer]] who was at some point the [[TransGal Champion Swoop Racer]]. Nasalle once witnessed a wind race during the [[Festival of the High Winds]] on [[Sevarcos II]], commenting on the fact that the participants were engaged in such a dangerous race just for the fun of it.<ref name="The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos" />

